{"tid":480831,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[入坑]幫朋友買左呢隻機械鍵盤，","createTime":"2017-11-26T14:05:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T10:45:45.000Z","uid":102587,"like":6,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6b943eddeb8577ed0a0d82bee1a54ec35ffd7fee","tid":480831,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:05:26.000Z","msg":"話說呢，佢買新電腦，又要有套新gear............下刪一千字........................<br />\n<br />\n總之就買要買機械鍵盤，最緊要有燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，好似初戀都要走肥走樣衰咁<br />\n<br />\n咁咪揀呢隻比佢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e3jmi4n7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe3jmi4n7&h=1e39fa5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n買左隻茶軸，本身我自己都係茶軸fans，咁冇理由個誘個fd 落坑買青軸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fneciwd0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffneciwd0&h=5fa9149e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即刻開盒、上個手，鬼叫你叫我幫你買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻用左無上蓋式設計，望幾&mdash;型棍，用會睇到 RGB Cherry軸 的透明外殼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dxbmt3vi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdxbmt3vi&h=627b12b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n後面都係有走線位，防滑膠，托腳咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ceb1h620\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fceb1h620&h=705c324f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一D 大鍵都係用衛星軸作穩定用途，<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fu0kcp8t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffu0kcp8t&h=3b27f35b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用左自己部Surface 著個燈先，好似可以裝個driver set 燈效，不過我都係過下手癮算，廢事裝個driver 又調燈又盛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/m0298ndq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fm0298ndq&h=8b536898&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原來粒LED燈 係系 Cherry RGB 軸個殼入面，咁樣D 光會透得靚D。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ka7ry15c\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fka7ry15c&h=eb9769d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n換個Corsair KEYCAP 落去，等佢玩 LOL就手D。我送既。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ux3zdy2m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fux3zdy2m&h=f558b8a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個QWER會有斜CUT 手感。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0l97ehom\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0l97ehom&h=f5caa0ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n換KEYCAP點少得PBT，換個 透光既，咁落手感同原裝的ABS差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，冇話特別實在左，睇黎原廠個用到打油先轉PBT都未遲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dc5e7fa1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdc5e7fa1&h=8d3ac5df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小記:<br />\n<br />\n個FD 初入坑，要求有燈，緊係拉著佢唔比佢上淘寶買 雙11 果D垃圾。<br />\n用得Cherry 又要RGB，暫時呢隻k60m plus算最平，仲要金屬面板，望落見得下人。<br />\n<br />\nKEYCAP 有二色ABS，襟用的，個磨砂面唔錯，手感有PBT咁。<br />\n<br />\n唔洗話比多少少上 Filco/leopold，等佢再慢慢先升級。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a97acfc1df003044722d89ee3caa3b4ecb00ef","tid":480831,"uid":97708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:19:21.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},{"pid":"cb05b03eb91f13f243b50b7611d1614ac34e07c9","tid":480831,"uid":151490,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T14:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"70d8a2f277eae5a0d7ec8e2f1654b0103ba7a4fa","tid":480831,"uid":27150,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:00:48.000Z","msg":"屌你一心砌條新女<br />\n個處就唔見左啦"},{"pid":"f85e69c15c2199eb271e815c852559b40b32898a","tid":480831,"uid":75139,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"見到D 注音都唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a020f70b42eae20f8b6db58ab32a11d522da0040","tid":480831,"uid":6636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:05:07.000Z","msg":"樓主打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681f37a45e5f69ea1dbf61da5e838c62b828c9dd","tid":480831,"uid":6636,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T19:05:08.000Z","msg":"樓主打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8e5ebadb6d25e490c88e6cde3f6912568197331","tid":480831,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T20:47:40.000Z","msg":"請善用起底功能"},{"pid":"071d7f163962db8445174fe41c2aa4c4f59c2774","tid":480831,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:42:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主打手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪要話 羅技好先唔打手 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4ae08128c76a57b30191a8666b68fbd415f139","tid":480831,"uid":102587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n8舊水"},{"pid":"13953be9e6a6282e154ebc8d25f9e5e229e5e4dc","tid":480831,"uid":12124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T04:11:37.000Z","msg":"打手死全家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15916bbe21615a34299012b80ad198cc9fbae8af","tid":480831,"uid":55593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:33:11.000Z","msg":"我都冇叫你換keycap"},{"pid":"e08eb8d5a055c20c3939ef220653bd48fc2584cf","tid":480831,"uid":108421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T10:45:45.000Z","msg":"呢啲款用1k買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}